      <p>Estimation of time consumption is important for a user-oriented method. Therefore, we evaluated the running time of BioSeq-Diabolo for protein remote homology detection on the proteins randomly extracted from SCOP1.75 database [<xref rid="pcbi.1011214.ref041" ref-type="bibr">41</xref>] (<ext-link xlink:href="http://bliulab.net/BioSeq-Diabolo/download/" ext-link-type="uri">http://bliulab.net/BioSeq-Diabolo/download/</ext-link>) with the following command line:</p>
